e views of practicing artists.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mrz 2022) 0aArt, Americany20th century. 0aArt, American. 0aWomen artistszUnited States. 7aART / Criticism.2bisacsh1 aBee, Susan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBee, Susan, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aBernstein, Charles, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChadwick, Whitney, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChin, Daryl, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCottingham, Laura, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCronin, Patricia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDrucker, Johanna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDrucker, Johanna.1 aFisher, Joel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrueh, Joanna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGreen, Vanalyne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHafif, Marcia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJones, Amelia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJones, Amelia.1 aKnechtel, Tom, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMcCoy, Ann, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMiller, Nancy, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNahas, Dominique, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNechvatal, Joseph, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPollack, Barbara, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPozzi, Lucio, econtributor.4ctb4https: